1
00:00:49,720 --> 00:00:51,280
Boss, what's wrong?

2
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:52,560
Yeah, tell us.

3
00:00:52,560 --> 00:00:54,620
We'll help you figure something out.

4
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:57,120
Forget it.

5
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:58,000
Just leave.

6
00:01:03,360 --> 00:01:04,160
Go.

7
00:01:15,960 --> 00:01:17,760
I'm so angry my makeup is ruined.

8
00:01:24,039 --> 00:01:24,720
Cangyue.

9
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:29,200
Cangyue.

10
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:29,840
Get lost.

11
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:32,160
I won't.

12
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:38,570
You won't leave, right?

13
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:40,800
If you don't leave, I'll throw you off.

14
00:01:40,800 --> 00:01:42,330
I won't leave even if you do.

15
00:02:09,440 --> 00:02:10,240
You didn't...

16
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:18,000
Don't move. Go back.

17
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:47,440
I'm leaving.

18
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,530
I'm really leaving.

19
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:19,860
What are you doing?

20
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,400
Alright.

21
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:26,640
So annoying.

22
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:29,260
Just say what you want to say quickly.

23
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:39,800
I'm sorry.

24
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:43,680
I'm sorry?

25
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:47,240
What? I have to get out just because you said so?

26
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:50,570
And I have to forgive you just because you said you're sorry?

27
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:53,440
I didn't know what was wrong with me.

28
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:55,040
I was a little out of control.

29
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,300
I apologize to you.

30
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:58,920
I'm sorry.

31
00:04:03,440 --> 00:04:04,680
Can you forgive me?

32
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,920
So are you free tonight?

33
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:32,240
This is the first person I killed with my own hands.

34
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:36,680
But my hands have long been stained with blood.

35
00:04:38,159 --> 00:04:41,480
I have let down too many people in my life.

36
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:43,640
Your Majesty.

37
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,280
Do it.

38
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:48,200
But... but he made no grave mistake.

39
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:51,560
If he can knock over a candlestick today,

40
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:55,480
he'll dare to set Zhaoyang Hall on fire tomorrow.

41
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:59,120
If you can't bring yourself to do it,

42
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:02,040
I'll have to execute his entire family for you.

43
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:05,120
You have to choose one.

44
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:11,120
Your Majesty, I grew up with you

45
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:13,040
and have seen countless splendors.

46
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,440
My life has been worth it.

47
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:31,660
Although you've always borne a bad name,

48
00:05:32,080 --> 00:05:33,000
this infamy

49
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:35,440
made the Grand Princess lower her guard against you.

50
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:36,500
For over ten years,

51
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,520
it kept you and Ayan

52
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:40,440
living safely in the palace.

53
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:42,040
That's enough.

54
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:45,280
But... but I'm afraid they'll say

55
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:47,850
that killing is addictive.

56
00:05:49,880 --> 00:05:51,320
When I killed him,

57
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:53,360
it felt very strange.

58
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:55,320
Very strange.

59
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:57,409
It's not your fault.

60
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:59,220
Zhou Hong deserved to die.

61
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:04,410
My life has been absurd.

62
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,080
Wealth and glory

63
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:08,980
have long made me a caged bird.

64
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:12,740
Those sleepless days and nights,

65
00:06:13,760 --> 00:06:15,220
looking at the starry sky,

66
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:18,200
hoping a star would fall on me.

67
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:25,040
Did that star fall?

68
00:06:30,760 --> 00:06:32,280
Ever since Ayue came,

69
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:35,490
I haven't been afraid anymore.

70
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:52,520
Player's game progress: 70%.

71
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:59,120
Thanks to His Majesty,

72
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:01,120
he helped us drive away the drought.

73
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:01,920
Exactly.

74
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:02,720
Our emperor,

75
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:04,240
I don't know when he changed his temper.

76
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,440
He used to collect a fifty percent tax,

77
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:07,320
now he only collects thirty percent.

78
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:08,440
The tyrant used to

79
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:09,280
do nothing good.

80
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:11,080
We commoners suffered the most.

81
00:07:11,520 --> 00:07:12,780
Things are better now.

82
00:07:12,840 --> 00:07:13,640
Some immortal from out of nowhere

83
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:14,900
must have cast a spell,

84
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:15,760
and made our emperor

85
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:17,040
act like a decent human again.

86
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:17,960
Exactly.

87
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:20,080
Look how good our lives are now.

88
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:21,560
Yuanyuan.

89
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:24,380
Are they talking about my royal brother?

90
00:07:24,840 --> 00:07:27,280
Yes, they are all praising His Majesty.

91
00:07:27,520 --> 00:07:29,240
My royal brother is amazing.

92
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:31,080
So many people like him.

93
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,880
When our A'yan grows up,

94
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:36,120
you should also become someone like His Majesty.

95
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:36,920
Okay?

96
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,040
Okay.

97
00:07:39,080 --> 00:07:40,010
Have some water.

98
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:41,840
Yuanyuan, eat.

99
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:27,360
Fortunately, Your Majesty sent someone to save me.

100
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:29,960
So the disaster relief went smoothly without any real danger.

101
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:31,620
You've worked hard, Teacher.

102
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,679
It is my duty.

103
00:08:34,039 --> 00:08:35,200
This way,

104
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:38,799
Your Majesty's prestige among the people has been largely restored.

105
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:40,840
The things you taught me when I was young,

106
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:42,640
I haven't forgotten any of them.

107
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,000
Oh, right.

108
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:47,320
A'yan has been fussing lately,

109
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:49,040
wanting to spend the Spring Festival with you.

110
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:51,170
Would you be willing to come, Teacher?

111
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:53,540
Is there no palace banquet this year?

112
00:08:57,800 --> 00:08:59,560
With natural disasters occurring year after year,

113
00:08:59,560 --> 00:09:01,090
the people are struggling.

114
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:03,760
The palace should be frugal.

115
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:07,320
We'll just gather together this year.

116
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:09,600
Just having a New Year's atmosphere is good enough.

117
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:11,730
Then I shall thank Your Majesty first.

118
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,800
Just now at the door,

119
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:15,400
I ran into the little prince.

120
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:16,960
He was pulling Eunuch Jingyuan,

121
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,840
insisting on going to the folk market to buy New Year goods.

122
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:21,920
He said he would give us some

123
00:09:21,920 --> 00:09:23,780
small folk gifts for the New Year.

124
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:24,600
Gifts?

125
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:27,290
What is he going to give?

126
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:30,640
I am really not sure about that.

127
00:09:32,160 --> 00:09:34,160
Does Your Majesty also want to go to the folk market

128
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:35,320
to pick out some gifts for Lady Cangyue

129
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:37,380
that are not available in the palace?

130
00:09:38,640 --> 00:09:40,120
Palace rewards and folk trinkets

131
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,040
are too cliché.

132
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:43,180
If I am going to give a gift,

133
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:45,680
I will give a unique one.

134
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:55,320
Thank you, brother.

135
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,840
I love it so much.

136
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:58,850
This is a gift

137
00:09:59,160 --> 00:10:00,880
for Miss Cangyue.

138
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:08,480
By the way, Yuanyuan,

139
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:11,040
didn't you say you'd give me a little airplane?

140
00:10:11,040 --> 00:10:12,280
Where is it?

141
00:10:15,520 --> 00:10:16,760
Airplane?

142
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:18,880
What is an airplane?

143
00:10:19,160 --> 00:10:21,160
I have never heard of it.

144
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:25,040
I heard it's something that can fly.

145
00:10:25,520 --> 00:10:26,920
I haven't seen it either.

146
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:28,800
I've been waiting for a month.

147
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:30,440
Yuanyuan, you went back on your word.

148
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:33,800
Rubik's cube, hot pot, airplane.
